snippet.title: American Truck Simulator - Western Star® 49X
snippet.description:
A tribute video celebrating a new free DLC expanding American Truck Simulator with the Western Star® 49X.

The most tested, durable, and toughest Western Star® truck to-date, the 49X is built to thrive in rugged environments and to take on anything. 

Western Star® is a trademark of Daimler Trucks North America LLC and is used under license to SCS Software s.r.o.
